<span class="label">Legally Speaking</span>
<h2>U.S. Copyright Office's Questions about Generative AI</h2>
<h6 class="subheader"></h6>
</div>
<hr class="dotted" />
<div id="articleFullText" class="col1 floatLeft firstCol">
<span class="byline">
By Pamela Samuelson
<br/>
Communications of the ACM,
March 2024,
Vol. 67 No. 3, Pages 25-28<br/>
10.1145/3637627<br/>
<a href="#comments">Comments</a>
</span>
