<figure>
<img alt="copyright symbols being fed into a crank machine, illustration" src="/system/assets/0004/7100/021624_CACMpg25_US-Copyright-Office1.large.jpg?1708108400&amp;1708108400" title="copyright symbols being fed into a crank machine, illustration" />
